::Magmatron::

    "Can you pick up my signal?" Magmatron called to the Maximal ship. He had 
his comm set to monitor all frequencies, Maximal and Predacon alike. He 
happened to be sitting in the Comm room when the message was sent. He hoped 
they could find him, they might be useful to make an alliance with. "If you 
can land as close as you can, the Predacons are in number down here, and we 
could use some help."
